reviews.content:
- Weak script;
- Too colorful;
- Too many frames per second;
- Too many people and without depth, forgettable and we don't care if they die or not;
- Some characters even looked really cool and it would have been nice if they had gone deeper into their story;
- People without charisma to take the place of epic actors;
- Tons of fan service with the only use is to cover lack of creativity;
- The only "chosen one" move is force push.

I almost left the movie theater
